des: "A simple light and sweet salad with goat cheese, dried cherries and walnuts. This dish reminds me of being on the beach."
ins: Toss the salad greens, raspberry vinaigrette, walnut pieces, and dried cherries together in a large bowl. Divide the salad into individual salad bowls or plates. Garnish each salad with two slices of goat cheese and a few strips of chicken breast.
